default Primates are highly intelligent animals with complex needs that can
default't be met in a home environment and can suffer greatly. 
defaultThere is considerable evidence to suggest that many keepers of pet primates lack the appropriate knowledge and/or facilities to adequately provide for their welfare. 
defaultSoulsbury et al., 2009 in their sc
defaultientific assessment of the suitability
default of primates as pets in the UK 
defaultconcluded that the practice should end.
